summary: Another in my Crests Mod On-going project.
descriptionHtml:
Clan Forbes Stormcloaks:

download, endorse if you like, give me feed back if not :) let me know how im doing so i can continue to improve my texture skill ;)

anyway, this was a request by GorillaWhizKid to make his Clans Colors overwrite the Original stormcloak rebels texture (and before anyone asks yes this will be incorporated into my \'Tartan Stormcloaks\' mod too because it looks AWESOME!)

so enjoy slaughtering imperial weaklings with the fierce warriors of Clan Forbes, or enjoy stepping up to the challenge of putting down these brave warriors with the legion? you decide ;)

as always, open to requests and also as always, you can use these textures so long as permission is asked and credit given.

Callaghan04
